<paragraph blockId="26.[160,1155,1093,1188]" box="[160,409,1093,1119]" pageId="26" pageNumber="291">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[160,409,1093,1119]" italics="true" pageId="26" pageNumber="291">External morphology</emphasis>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="26.[160,1155,1093,1188]" pageId="26" pageNumber="291">Shell helicoidal, conical, with reticulated microsculpture, orange due to digestive gland seen by transparency. Wing flaps broad, extending over the length of the shell.</paragraph>
